        public boolean isPrintListViewOnly()

        true if only the list view panel on a page should be printed

      • getListViewTitle

        public java.lang.String getListViewTitle(java.lang.String listViewWidgetId)
        Fetches a title for a given list view if it has been overridden with addListViewTitle. This is primarily used to apply a title to search results list views which do not have titles (anonymous) because they are output independent of the page. (PrintListViewOnly property set)
        Parameters:
        listViewWidgetId - listViewWidgetId ID of the list view widget that the title caption is being sought
        Returns:
        title caption of given list view widget
